 ⚡ Quick Start (run on your VPS as root)

      # 1. SSH into your VPS

      ssh root@YOUR_VPS_IP


      # 2. Download & prepare the installer

      curl -o ~/kader.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/youngkmd/Freedom/refs/heads/main/installer.sh

      chmod +x ~/kader.sh

      ln -sf ~/kader.sh /usr/local/bin/k


      # 3. Launch the installer

      k
    
Follow interactive prompts: enter license key, select Windows version (41-47), type YES to confirm. After 10–30 min, your VPS reboots into Windows with RDP ready.

