 🖥️ First login — VNC Notice (Contabo / DigitalOcean)
On some providers, RDP won't work immediately. Open VNC/console from control panel, login as Administrator / Teddysun.com. A network configuration script runs in background (~60 sec). After that, RDP is available. One‑time step only.
 Most providers work without VNC intervention, but if RDP fails after reboot — use the VNC method above.

